title: Photos released of Chinaâs first domestic aircraft carrier
content:
A photo of China's first domestically made aircraft carrier during its fifth sea trial. (Photo/CCTV)
	Photos have been released of China's first domestically manufactured aircraft carrier on its recent fifth sea trial.
	The trial tested the carrier's command and control system and battle performance, with the vessel completing tests of its mooring, power, battle and security system.
